include_once '../config/db.php'; // adjust path depending on folder


2️⃣ Optional Bill-Level Tax & Discounts

Products Table: discount_allowed + product_discount (optional)

Sales Table: bill_discount + bill_tax

Sales Items Table: discount (optional item-level discount)

POS logic in cashier/pos.php & api/save_sale.php will need to use:

subtotal = sum((product_price - item_discount) * qty)
bill_tax = subtotal * tax_rate / 100  // if enabled
grand_total = subtotal + bill_tax - bill_discount



3️⃣ Folder/Includes Usage

Header, Footer, Sidebar: includes/header.php, includes/footer.php, includes/sidebar.php

All pages (admin/*, cashier/*) should include:

<?php include '../includes/header.php'; ?>
<?php include '../includes/sidebar.php'; ?>
<!-- Page Content Here -->
<?php include '../includes/footer.php'; ?>


JS files:

pos.js → POS cart logic, calculation of subtotal, discounts, tax, grand total

main.js → general scripts like search, alerts

alerts.js → notifications / sweetalerts

